                        <p style="font-size: 10px"> 
                            Section IV. In case there is a request for interment on the lot purchased by the BUYER, interment shall only be allowed if the total contract price or the unpaid balance and interment fee have been paid in full.  
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 10px; margin-left: 30px"> 
