                            made by the BUYER from his previous lot/crypt shall be credited to his new contract.  Other charges (processing fee, dis-interment
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 10px"> 
                            Section VII.	 Any omissions and/or changes on location of property as well as survey matter not consistent with the sales plan; the company 
